Karin Viard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karin_Viard 0 Karin Viard (French: [ka.ʁin vjaʁ]; born 24 January 1966) is a multi-award-winning French actress. She made her film debut in Tatie Danielle in 1990. She has appeared in films such as Delicatessen, L'Emploi du temps, Adultère, mode d'emploi and La parenthèse enchantée. Viard was a member of the 2003 Cannes Film Festival jury. Karin_Viard ( French : [_ka.ʁin_vjaʁ_] ; born_24_January_1966 ) is a_multi-award-winning_French_actress .
